data.description: Welcome to Echo Farms! This charming two-story house is the perfect blend of vintage appeal and modern upgrades. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, this home offers ample space for your family's needs. Step inside to discover the stunning updates that make this home truly exceptional. With brand new windows, garage doors, HVAC, and a roof replaced in 2019, you can enjoy peace of mind knowing that the major upgrades have already been taken care of.The spacious layout of this home ensures that every family member has their own private retreat. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfort and convenience for all. The master suite, with its own ensuite bathroom, offers a tranquil oasis where you can unwind after a long day.The main level features a thoughtfully designed floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living spaces. The well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern appliances, is perfect for culinary adventures and creating lasting memories. Entertain guests in the formal dining room or gather around the fireplace in the cozy living room on cooler evenings.Outside, you'll find a beautifully landscaped yard, providing a serene backdrop for outdoor activities and relaxation. The Echo Farms neighborhood offers a peaceful setting with tree-lined streets, perfect for leisurely walks or bike rides.Conveniently located, this home is just a short distance from schools, shopping centers, and recreational facilities, ensuring that everything you need is within easy reach.Don't miss this opportunity to own a meticulously maintained home with updated features in the desirable Echo Farms community. Schedule your private showing today and envision the endless possibilities that await you in this delightful residence!
